name: A Calm Afternoon
description:
Marsi, the cat, is having some fun in the kitchen. Wondering what she is up to? Hmm...that tree looks familiar...I wonder if she knows Sharo?
This piece is part of Vegzi's Hiragana Art World. Collectors from primary market get special NFT #41 and #9 from Vegzi's Hiragana Collection.
